Splatoon 2 is an upcoming third-person shooter video game developed and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo Switch .
It is the sequel to the 2015 Wii U title , Splatoon , and is a team-based third-person shooter which is playable by up to eight players in online four-versus-four matches .
The game was announced in January 2017 , and will be released worldwide in July 2017 .